<br>
Would he have launched a public-relations campaign downplaying the toxicity of fish tainted with PCBs, a compound banned worldwide? Would he have spent large amounts of shareholder money on a lobbying campaign to amend the federal Superfund law to limit industry liability for the costs of toxic cleanups?<br>
